user.biography:
Making luxury accessible.
18k Gold plated – Waterproof – Free shipping
Designed in Switzerland🇨🇭

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by LEO MAZZOTTI in Rome, Italy. May be an image of sky.

node.text:
Live the Dolce Vita 🕊
Did you see our exclusive deal of today : 20% OFF on our WHOLE website with the code: AUGUST20 

But be carefull, the offer is ONLY available until midnight so don't wait any longer! #LeoMazzotti

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by LEO MAZZOTTI on August 18, 2021. May be an image of jewelry.

node.text:
Timeless, waterproof and made to last 🌿
We can't get enough of the how gorgeous our new Louise necklace looks with our other pieces. #LeoMazzotti

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by LEO MAZZOTTI on August 16, 2021. May be an image of jewelry.

node.text:
NOW ONLINE: TWO NEW JEWELRY 🌿
Seduce summer with new minimalist details - The Celie Bracelet and the Louise Necklace. Finished with a 18k gold plated layer, these pieces  will be a perfect match with your daily outfit. 

Tell us in the comments which pieces do you like the most : the bracelet or the necklace ? #LeoMazzotti

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by LEO MAZZOTTI on August 15, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and flower.

node.text:
NEW JEWELRY TOMORROW - Get a taste of what's coming tomorrow 🌿
We have designed 2 new jewelry for you to accompany you throughout this summer and add a special something to your style - Available in 18k Gold plated, 18k Rose Gold plated and Silver ! 

Are you as excited as we are ? #LeoMazzotti

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by LEO MAZZOTTI on August 13, 2021. May be an image of jewelry.

node.text:
Small details make a big difference 💫 
Some classic pieces which never go out of style. Waterproof and guaranteed for life, our jewelry is designed in our offices in Switzerland to provide you with quality jewelry at reasonable prices. #LeoMazzotti
